data.description: This impeccably maintained ranch-style residence beckons a new owner! Situated mere steps from the beautiful Pueblo Country Club, step inside to revel in the thoughtfully updated abode that seamlessly blends modern upgrades with original charm. Nice classic touches like built-in storage and original coved ceilings keep the classic feel. The original one-car garage has undergone a transformation into a master suite, featuring an attached laundry, spacious walk-in closet, and a 3/4 bath. Don't worry about the garage space – a colossal three-car garage awaits at the alley, complemented by backyard egress and RV parking possibilities. This home, nestled close to shopping and amenities, is a rare find that demands attention.
